" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu1ZR049.png&h=eb32d87c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ue3vxbQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUe3vxbQ.png&h=e3f09329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁都算 佢今日突然話AMAZON果邊停左佢地個AC 佢地呢幾日既單全部reject晒 仲俾左個好求其既&quot;官方&quot;電郵我地睇 但個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">電郵內容極度不清晰</span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WbiO3g2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbiO3g2.png&h=882f8868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/16DfJg3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F16DfJg3.png&h=88bad498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢之後補左話咩今日去現場派 但其實現場派呢件事根本就風險大成效低 人地係現場打仗咁你會唔會係拎住個喼走去派野？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFiCWKj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFiCWKj.png&h=53775c80&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXQNzwh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXQNzwh.png&h=5c0d95d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我無試過FC唔到亦都無得FC件事究竟係真定假 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嗰三萬幾四萬蚊gift card會唔會係消失係一個無名無ac no.無根據既email到</span></span> 大家可以諗一諗 如果真係有心想幫 不如真係FC左可靠既group先 幫錯人就無謂 <br />\n<br />\n最後補多張 啱啱我都收到同一個email <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/faVmDZN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfaVmDZN.png&h=8b65e3bc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:19:05.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以唔好咁撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家好多扑街發災難財。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T22:18:46.000Z","msg":"哇 同禮義廉有得比"},{"pid":"d5962c9a2da9186ae856cf4e3dbfaf473421a34b","tid":1570244,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl